      "full_name": "Sovfracht JSC",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "Sovfracht JSC is a Russian shipping company providing logistical support to the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation. In particular, Sovfracht JSC functions as a key node in military transportation networks of Russian cargo vessels shipping North Korean armaments from Pyongyang to military facilities in the Russian port of Dunai. Subsequently, North Korean munitions transported by Sovfracht JSC are transferred to weapons depots on Russia’s western border to be deployed in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}